Distribution.
Symmachia falcistriga
is known from the Amazon basin with records in Colombia (Nielsen & Salazar 2015), Brazil ( Acre , Amazonas, Rondônia , Pará) and Bolivia ( Stichel 1914 ;
Gareca et al. 2006
) ( Fig. 153 ). It is expected that this taxon also occurs at least in Mato Grosso , Brazil , Peru , and Ecuador .
